title: BRIEF-Precinct Properties New Zealand Posts ‍H1 Net Profit After Tax Of NZ$17.7 Mln

organizations.name: reuters) - precinct properties new zealand ltd

text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Precinct Properties New Zealand Ltd :
* ‍DIVIDEND GUIDANCE FOR FY18 MAINTAINED AT 5.80 NZ CPS​ * H1 NET OPERATING INCOME NZ$38.2 MILLION VERSUS NZ$38.8 MILLION
* ‍H1 NET PROFIT AFTER TAX NZ$17.7 MILLION VERSUS NZ$39.1 MILLION
* EARNINGS GUIDANCE FOR FY18 UNCHANGED AT 6.30 NZ CPS * SECOND-QUARTER DIVIDEND OF 1.45 NZ CENTS PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
